title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
OB: When opening the hyperlink builder, the title does not display as 'Hyperlink Options'.
EB: When opening the hyperlink builder, the title should display as 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: 1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'. 2. Open the hyperlink builder and observe the title.
